datafield.subfield: Record Group 2, Operating and Maintenance Department records,

Southern Pacific Railroad Company records are arranged in 7 record groups: 1. Board of Directors records; 2. Operating and Maintenance Department records; 3. Mechanical Department records; 4. Accounting Department records; 5. Office of the Secretary records; 6. Legal Department records; and 7. Real Estate Department records. Each record group has its own catalog record. For a full description and to page individual items see the record for that group.
Record Group 2 consists of 2 subgroups: subgroup 1, Maintenance of Way Engineering Division records, 1889-1993; subgroup 2, Design and Construction Engineering Division records, 1907-1997.
San Diego & Arizona Eastern Railway Company.
